### Auth Infrastructure

#### [NEW] [middleware.ts](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/Shahirun/Cravely/apps/web/middleware.ts)
- Protect `/chat`, `/profile`, `/onboarding` → redirect to `/login`
- Redirect authenticated users away from `/login` → `/chat`
- Allow public: `/`, `/login`, `/auth/callback`
- Use `@supabase/ssr` `createServerClient` with cookie handling

#### [NEW] [route.ts](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/Shahirun/Cravely/apps/web/app/auth/callback/route.ts)
- Exchange OAuth code for session
- Check `users` table — new user → `/onboarding`, existing → `/chat`
- Error → `/login?error=auth_failed`

#### [NEW] [user.ts](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/Shahirun/Cravely/apps/web/lib/supabase/user.ts)
- `createUserProfile(supabase, userId, fullName, cityId?)` — insert into `users`
- `saveUserPreferences(supabase, userId, dietary, cuisineNames, neighborhoodNames)` — lookup IDs + upsert into [user_preferences](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/Shahirun/Cravely/apps/api/app/tools/search.py#243-265)

